Name: stage1
StageDescription: The animal friends set out from the entrance of the small forest. Their first enemy is a hungry crow.

Name: stage2
StageDescription: Crossing the lush meadow, they must avoid the interference of wriggling earthworms. Keep the supplies safe!

Name: stage3
StageDescription: While crossing the bridge, beware of the fish swarm’s attacks. The waters are full of danger.

Name: stage4
StageDescription: On the windy hill, be on guard against sudden strikes from hawks. Teamwork is crucial here.

Name: stage5
StageDescription: In the darkened woods, the threat of wolves begins. Move quietly and carefully.

Name: stage6
StageDescription: Around the serene lake, hidden crocodiles lurk. Protect the supplies and tread carefully.

Name: stage7
StageDescription: On the uneven rocky path, fend off attacks from stag beetles. Stay calm and focused.

Name: stage8
StageDescription: The beautiful plains are home to hidden snakes. Don’t let your guard down!

Name: stage9
StageDescription: Around the slippery and dangerous waterfall, a bear may appear. Stay alert!
